CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

December 23, 2002

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2002-0326. Disciplinary Counsel v. Westgate.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that Gregory A. Westgate, Attorney Registration No. 0036768, last known business address in Lorain, Ohio, be found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of August 21, 2002, to wit, failure to surrender his certificate of admission and failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before September 20, 2002.
